Audit: fix remaining script/ScreenGui name-collision lookups

Full codebase pass for the same class of bug as the HUD (LocalScript name ==
ScreenGui name, so FindFirstChild can return the script):

- BracketController: was resolving the BracketScreen by name and could grab the
  script — cup countdown/result updates silently no-op'd. Now resolves the real
  ScreenGui.
- UIController.getGui: same; now prefers a real ScreenGui match (makes its
  redundant HUD/nav/screen logic correct as a backup to the self-contained HUD).

Verified clean (no bugs): CardService (rarity/guarantee/squad-dupe security),
MonetizationService (idempotent ProcessReceipt), TradeService (atomic, re-validated
swap), Collection/Squad/Bracket/Shop screens (self-contained, close buttons,
self-subscribe), and MatchdaySchedule timestamps (2026 dates correct).

